itunes:title: Kardashian Recap Episode 3- Live from New York!
title: Kardashian Recap Episode 3- Live from New York!
description:
In today's episode we're recapping episode 3- Live from New York!  We finally get to see the SNL episode, Kim's sex tape is finally put to rest, Kris is adamant on taking Khloe on a tour of her old NYC stomping grounds and final plans are made for Kravis engagement!

Throw us some fries Kendall and Kyle! ;)
